ZH: 他俯身下跪向母亲道歉。
EN: He knelt down and apologized to his mother.

ZH: 她俯身捡起地上的钱包。
EN: She bent down to pick up the wallet from the ground.

ZH: 我们俯身聆听老师的教导。
EN: We bow down to listen to the teacher's guidance.

ZH: 他俯身低头，不敢看我的眼睛。
EN: He bows his head, unable to look into my eyes.

ZH: 她小心翼翼地俯身抱起了小猫。
EN: She carefully stooped down and picked up the kitten.

ZH: 在过道上行走时，请俯身小心。
EN: When walking in the aisle, please stoop down carefully.

ZH: 他俯身关切地询问我是否没事。
EN: He stooped down and asked me with concern if I was okay.

ZH: 她俯身向老人伸出援助之手。
EN: She stooped down and extended a helping hand to the elderly person.

ZH: 他俯身检查了车底的损坏情况。
EN: He stooped down to inspect the damage underneath the car.

ZH: 我们俯身观察小花朵的精细结构。
EN: We stoop down to observe the delicate structure of the small flowers.

ZH: 那个冒险者勇敢地俯身进入了黑暗洞穴。
EN: The adventurer courageously stooped down and entered the dark cave.

ZH: 他俯身在地面上写下了一行字。
EN: He bent down and wrote a line of words on the ground.

ZH: 她俯身拾起掉在地上的书籍。
EN: She stooped down to pick up the books that fell on the ground.

ZH: 他们俯身观察鸟巢里的小鸟。
EN: They stoop down to observe the baby birds inside the nest.

ZH: 在打扫地板时，要俯身捡起垃圾。
EN: When cleaning the floor, bend down to pick up the trash.

ZH: 他俯身提起行李袋，准备登上火车。
EN: He stooped down to lift the baggage, getting ready to board the train.

ZH: 妈妈俯身给我系鞋带。
EN: Mom stooped down to tie my shoelaces.

ZH: 孩子们俯身抓起沙滩上的贝壳。
EN: The children stooped down to grab seashells on the beach.

ZH: 那只猫俯身闻了闻花朵的香气。
EN: The cat bent down to sniff the fragrance of the flower.

ZH: 她俯身捧起碎片，准备修复花瓶。
EN: She stooped down and picked up the pieces, preparing to fix the vase.

ZH: 当爸爸弯下腰俯身时，我跳了起来，让他背着我走。
EN: When Dad bent down and stooped, I jumped up and asked him to carry me.
